{"tid":457403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本公寓9死命案　附近住戶不願搬「想繼續住」因租太平","createTime":"2017-11-03T23:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T04:51:10.000Z","uid":82845,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b095dc1e24e567793b1035a6d80e2a38b9ef63f1","tid":457403,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:25:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bkA_hXeVgls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbkA_hXeVgls&d=dnuc5FFUOwoKRKE3OsNxAzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=3afb7ab6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bkA_hXeVgls</a><br />\n<br />\n日本神奈川縣座間市發生9屍命案，27歲嫌犯白石隆浩在8~10月短短2個月間殺了9人更分屍，原本以為同間公寓的住戶會急著搬走，沒想到一戶都沒走全部留著，<span style=\"color: red;\">「租金便宜附近又便利，想繼續住」。</span><br />\n<br />\n據《日刊SPA》報導，座間市公寓30日發生9屍命案震撼日本，同棟住戶搬走、房價下跌似乎是可預見之事，連網路上也有不少同情公寓管理者的聲音，沒想到事發3天後，意外的住戶沒有人想搬走。<br />\n<br />\n管理該間公寓的管理公司職員A先生指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">「事件後，想要退租的電話一通都沒有，反而都反問『可以不要搬走嗎』、『可以繼續住嗎？』除了大吃一驚外也覺得他們很有勇氣」。</span><br />\n<br />\nA先生提道「大家都覺得這邊租金便宜，生活機能也便利，發生事件後反而擔心問『會把公寓拆了嗎？』」。該間公寓是建造完成30年的木造2樓建築，是附有閣樓、專租給單身者的套房，房租加管理費只要22000日圓(約1500港幣)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白石隆浩是在8月下旬入住，A先生回憶「白石隆浩都會打招呼，誰看到都會認為是個好青年，當時他急著注入，現在想起來的確也怪怪的」。報導指出，白石隆浩入住2個月間殺了9人，分解遺體後放在室內，有著奇怪的異臭，A先生說「目前看過不少孤獨死跟自殺現場，跟那些案件比這邊不算臭，雖然的確有點異味就是了」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生活既壓力仲恐怖過見鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇片間屋就係地鐵隔離"},{"pid":"6f5924de47bfda0ce14dcb821b1f24d9710e5169","tid":457403,"uid":5267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:41:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97c53664665d2181fac5fbe53d587b63fac8e9b4","tid":457403,"uid":17616,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:48:15.000Z","msg":"22000咁平俾我都唔走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家住緊個度要65000重要係share house <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e973a5a62f538aaacbb1a14087644b4611e7c5b","tid":457403,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:48:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eae781ac25b99c6c7c94458e16b41c55047dbbfd","tid":457403,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:48:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d97dca54a6f375fe4afc84185d92de23c5ad69e9","tid":457403,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd21a83e95ea9c860024a12ecccba8b499c11933","tid":457403,"uid":895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:33:35.000Z","msg":"A先生說「目前看過不少孤獨死跟自殺現場，跟那些案件比這邊不算臭，雖然的確有點異味就是了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986733b9e03829e4da6508ef141a6280d7518b1b","tid":457403,"uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:34:47.000Z","msg":"死多一千個一百個我都唔走"},{"pid":"cc4ffbf41071d8bbe1192c2bb4f368972b401ffc","tid":457403,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A先生說「目前看過不少孤獨死跟自殺現場，跟那些案件比這邊不算臭，雖然的確有點異味就是了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能滴哂屍水佢都唔會走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8845d5732afb28b6c2e3adaf615ea364148c050a","tid":457403,"uid":111965,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21317681_1551876024870305_5867876190344193781_n.png?oh=46714b987869dcd38997a03b76eb8c04&amp;oe=5AB022FB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F2131